newsitem.title: USA: Muni dealers traded $1.09 bln bonds Tuesday - MSRB.
newsitem.headline: Muni dealers traded $1.09 bln bonds Tuesday - MSRB.

text.p: Municipal bond dealers traded $1.09 billion of bonds Tuesday on 3,574 trades, the Municipal Securities Rulemaking Board said.
A total of 2,135 individual issues changed hands, with 88 of those trading four or more times, MSRB said, citing figures from an automated clearance system of interdealer trades.
For more detailed MSRB data, double-click on JJK501 --U.S. Municipal Desk, 212-859-1650
